  "title": "Project Executive (Events & Exhibitions)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>SPACElogic Pte Ltd is a young & dynamic organisation that specialises in interior design & fit-out, permanent exhibits & display, signage & environmental graphics and event & exhibition projects.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Support project management by coordinating site activities, liaising with vendors, and ensuring quality and regulatory compliance to deliver successful interior fit-out and exhibition projects.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support the Project Manager in coordinating site activities to ensure smooth production and execution of projects</li><li>Liaise with vendors to enforce quality standards and timely delivery of materials and services</li><li>Monitor project budgets and schedules to maintain cost control and timely completion</li><li>Ensure compliance with safety, building, and regulatory requirements throughout project phases</li><li>Manage site operations including conducting and attending site meetings to resolve issues proactively</li><li>Collaborate closely with designers to align project execution with design intent and client expectations</li><li>Prepare detailed reports, attend project meetings, and assist in tender documentation processes</li><li>Adhere to project scheduling requirements including documentation, commissioning, and handover</li><li>Maintain quality control by managing sub-contractors and suppliers effectively</li><li>Identify critical project paths, anticipate potential challenges, and propose practical solutions</li><li>Assess resource requirements and allocate responsibilities to optimize team performance</li><li>Administer routine management reporting and provide timely project updates to stakeholders</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Knowledge of structural, audiovisual (AV), and mechanical & electrical (M&E) systems to support integrated project delivery</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office applications to facilitate project documentation and communication</li><li>Ability to work effectively within a collaborative team environment to achieve project goals</li></ul>",
